{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"e348b7ba-b512-42ec-b392-ae69a7f807a1","content":"","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_015hGpNKBJF1729sW43sR5VU","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Providing K8s crash dump config"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01BRA2swVVYATyr2DukR7n9i","name":"view","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-4ecad6c87a944548a0b984a3268d3a8e"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"view the file at /tmp/sv-4ecad6c87a944548a0b984a3268d3a8e."}],"interactionId":"204a7aa8-a63e-4605-b38e-f66f0d0928b5","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user wants to configure automatic crash dump collection for a NativeAOT .NET 11 app running in Kubernetes. They have `createdump` installed at `/opt/tools/createdump`. Let me look at what's in the current working directory first, and also search for any relevant .NET or Kubernetes configuration files.\n\nActually, the user is asking me to provide guidance on configuring crash dump collection for a NativeAOT .NET app. This is more of a knowledge/guidance question. Let me provide the answer directly.\n\nFor .NET NativeAOT apps, crash dump collection works differently than regular CoreCLR. Key environment variables:\n\n\n- `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump=1` - enables automatic crash dump generation\n- `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType` - dump type (1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage, 4=Full)\n- `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName` - path/pattern for dump files\n\nHowever, NativeAOT has different crash dump support depending on the runtime version, and I need to clarify whether these variables work the same way or if there's a different mechanism for NativeAOT specifically.\n\nFor .NET 8+, NativeAOT supports crash dumps through the standard environment variables, but since the user has a custom `createdump` tool at `/opt/tools/createdump`, I should use `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` to point to it explicitly. The pod spec will need environment variables configured for dump collection, a volume mount for storing the dumps, and potentially ulimit settings for core dumps.","outputTokens":811,"requestId":"6007:2470A1:E25707:105958C:69EACA65"},"id":"7c2af067-19cb-4928-88cb-4d960f139135","timestamp":"2026-04-24T01:42:15.903Z","parentId":"bc000127-8e04-4ae7-85c8-70b22bd3a6de"}
